Package: linearclassifers
Title: Functions for kNN Classification
Version: 0.0.0.1003
Authors@R: person("Samantha", "Dalton", , "samantha.dalton@barcelonagse.eu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for kNN classfication.  Includes a function to calculate distances, a function to compute classifications based on distances, and a function to evaluate the best k to use for your dataset.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.1), assertthat, doParallel, foreach
License: See LICENSE
LazyData: true
